<p><strong>文章：</strong> SCP-3939 (<em>[编号保留，以待研究员]</em>)</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608737405" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;">Croquembouche</a></span></p>
<p><strong>致谢：</strong> <span class="error-inline"><em>Baseplate-Actual</em> does not match any existing user name</span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3208919); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608737405" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3208919); return false;">taylor_itkin</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608737405" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;">Tanhony</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1422059); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1422059&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608737405" alt="MayD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1422059)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1422059); return false;">MayD</a></span></p>
<p>这是一篇多选择故事。每一页底部的箭头形状的链接选项表示其可将您带到另一页中。完整阅读一整条这篇SCP的故事线将花费大约15分钟。并不期望您会再读一遍。</p>
